OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,FGreggs is planning to open its first
OL,7,Fever international outlet at Tenerife
OL,8,FSouth airport as the company looks to
OL,9,Fexpand its chain of shops.
OL,11,FHolidaymakers can get their hands on
OL,12,Fthe Newcastle-based firm's popular
OL,13,Fsausage roll at the airport later this
OL,14,Fmonth.
OL,16,FA Spanish omelette roll will be
OL,17,Favailable as part of the breakfast
OL,18,Fmenu alongside freshly squeezed orange
OL,19,Fjuice, prepared and bottled in-shop
OL,20,Fdaily, "giving customers a refreshing
OL,21,Ftaste of island life", the baker said.
OL,26,@|D@HOU}D@UO]
