FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,FGreggs chief executive Roisin Currie
OL,7,Fsaid: "Tenerife South Airport is a hub
OL,8,Ffor millions of UK and international
OL,9,Fpassengers each year, making it the
OL,10,Fideal location to test spreading our
OL,11,Fwings in an overseas setting.
OL,13,F"It's an exciting milestone for Greggs
OL,14,Fas we bring a slice of home to the
OL,15,FCanaries, and we're confident our
OL,16,Fgreat-value offering will resonate
OL,17,Fjust as well under the Spanish sun as
OL,18,Fit does on the UK high street."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
