OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,FGreggs last operated shops abroad in
OL,7,FBelgium in 2008, but said Tenerife was
OL,8,F"the ideal location to test spreading
OL,9,Four wings in an overseas setting".
OL,11,FTenerife South airport welcomes around
OL,12,F13 million holiday-makers every year,
OL,13,Fwith around 50% flying to and from the
OL,14,FUK.
OL,16,FGreggs said the location made it the
OL,17,F"perfect way to round off a trip
OL,18,Fwithout breaking the bank".
OL,20,FThe shop will also offer seating for
OL,21,Fup to 92 customers.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@aO]yD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
