OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,FWhile the exact date for the opening
OL,7,Fis not yet set, Greggs said the shop
OL,8,Fin the international departures area
OL,9,Fof the airport will stock a range of
OL,10,Fbakes, rolls and sweet treats, as well
OL,11,Fas sandwiches.
OL,13,FJavier Cagigal, chief executive of
OL,14,FLagardere Travel Retail Spain and
OL,15,FPortugal, said: "We're delighted to
OL,16,Fpartner with Greggs to bring such a
OL,17,Fwell-loved brand into Tenerife South
OL,18,FAirport for the very first time.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,F"As passengers head home, this new
OL,7,Fopening gives them a familiar,
OL,8,Fcomforting choice in departures `
OL,9,Fwhether that's a last treat, a relaxed
OL,10,Fsit-down moment or something to ease
OL,11,Fthe journey home."
OL,13,FGreggs has opened 41 stores this year,
OL,14,Fwhile closing 21, and aims to open a
OL,15,Fnet total 120 over the year.
OL,17,FThe company now runs 2,759 outlets and
OL,18,Fbosses says they hope to cash in on
OL,19,Fthe millions of people passing through
OL,20,Fthe Spanish airport each year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,FGreggs has also toasted to improving
OL,7,Fsales over the year as it shakes up
OL,8,Fits menu and targets new shops, but
OL,9,Fwarned that it could be facing higher
OL,10,Fcosts if the Iran war rumbles on.
OL,12,FIn an update to investors, the firm
OL,13,Fsaid sales in company-managed shops,
OL,14,Frather than franchises, increased by
OL,15,F2.5% in the first 19 weeks of 2026,
OL,16,Fcompared like for like with the same
OL,17,Fperiod last year.
OL,19,FTotal sales, which includes new shop
OL,20,Fopenings, were up by 7.4% year on year
OL,21,Fto #800 million.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Greggs said it was
OL,7,Fmonitoring the situation in the Middle
OL,8,FEast amid rising energy costs.
OL,10,FThe company warned that a "prolonged"
OL,11,Fconflict means it, along with other
OL,12,Ffood retailers, "will likely see
OL,13,Fhigher overall cost inflation through
OL,14,Fthe end of 2026 and into 2027".
OL,16,FNonetheless, Greggs said it was
OL,17,Fappealing to customers looking for
OL,18,Fvalue-for-money in the "uncertain
OL,19,Fenvironment".
OL,26,@rD@[OUrD@eO]tD@QOUvD@^O]zD@XOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
