PN,42308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778591472
OL,3,CGreggs to open only international
OL,4,Coutlet as chain expands
OL,6,FGreggs said new menu items like its
OL,7,Fchicken roll ` an alternative to the
OL,8,Fstaple sausage roll ` and its range of
OL,9,Fmatcha drinks were proving popular,
OL,10,Fwhile appealing to new and younger
OL,11,Fcustomers.
OL,13,FIt has also been adding healthier
OL,14,Fitems to its menu to cater to growing
OL,15,Fdemand for nutritious and protein-rich
OL,16,Ffoods including a range of salads,
OL,17,Fwith a new chicken Caesar salad
OL,18,Flaunching last week.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
